Colombia Central Bank Bought $440 Million in Market in August

-- B y   B l a k e   S c h m i d t
-- 
2011-09-12T21:54:36Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-12/colombia-central-bank-bought-440-million-in-market-in-august.html
Colombia ’s central bank bought $440
million in the  currency market  through auctions last month.  Banco de la Republica also said on its website that it
didn’t buy or sell peso-denominated bonds, known as TES, last
month. At the end of August, the bank held 1.1 trillion pesos
($604 million) of peso bonds, according to the statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blake Schmidt in Bogota at 
